text: Towanda is the name of several places in the United States: *Towanda, Illinois *Towanda, Kansas *Pennsylvania: **Communities: ***Towanda, Pennsylvania, a borough in Bradford County ***Towanda Township, Pennsylvania, a township in Bradford County ***North Towanda Township, Pennsylvania, a township in Bradford County **Streams: ***Towanda Creek, a tributary of the Susquehanna River ***South Branch Towanda Creek, a tributary of Towanda Creek
title: Towanda
